The paper discusses the need for privacy-aware design tools for IoT applications, which falls under the category of cybersecurity (cs.CR). The paper also discusses the challenges in software engineering processes for IoT applications, which could be categorized under information retrieval (cs.IR) and software engineering (cs.SE). The paper also highlights the importance of privacy compliance, which could be categorized under cyber law (cs.CY) and social and information networks (cs.SI).
